      "message": "[Critical] Line 130: pluginData[\"bodyOverwrite\"] is trusted directly as the displayed message body. If plugin-provided content has different trust or formatting guarantees than normal message body content, this can expose injected markup/links or misleading content in the chat view. Please normalize/sanitize it through the same path used for message bodies, or document and enforce that plugins must provide already-safe plain text before assigning it to body.",
