      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 139: Edited-message bodyOverwrite is read from the edition map, while the new top-level pluginData field is modeled separately on SwarmMessage. If the daemon represents plugin metadata consistently as pluginData, edition-level plugin data may not be present as a flat \"bodyOverwrite\" key here, causing previousBodies to show/edit the raw body while the current message shows the overwrite. Please confirm the daemon payload shape and parse edition plugin data consistently.",
      "revId": "b9fe38eff944a54922b01848e6551b5bdd08ddfc",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
