      "writtenOn": "2026-06-18T14:53:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 114: Adding pluginData to the serialized SwarmMessage structure changes the D-Bus wire signature unconditionally. This can break clients built or run against a daemon that still emits the previous structure, which is especially relevant because the project supports external daemon builds. Please gate this with an interface/version compatibility check or keep backward-compatible deserialization for the old shape before reading pluginData.",
      "revId": "b9fe38eff944a54922b01848e6551b5bdd08ddfc",
